WHO   — Loial — the Ogier who went Outside, the author
WHAT  — an Ogier, one of the long-lived, tree-loving folk, ninety years young and called hasty by his elders
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the Ogier and the worldly peoples — the long-lived, tree-loving folk  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
